<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Order Cancellation Notice - Restaurant</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #e74c3c; /* Red color indicating cancellation */
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .order-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .order-id {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .order-status {
      color: #e74c3c; /* Red color for cancellation status */
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .restaurant-info {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2980b9; /* Blue color for restaurant details */
    }

    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Order Cancellation Notification</h1>
    <div class="order-details">
      <p class="order-id">Order ID: <%= @order.id %></p>
      <p class="order-status">Status: <strong>Cancelled</strong></p>
      <p class="restaurant-info">Restaurant: <%= @order.dish.restaurant.user.name %></p>
    </div>

    <p>This is to inform you that the following order has been cancelled:</p>

    <p><strong>Customer Name:</strong> <%= @order.client.user.name %></p>
    <p><strong>Customer Phone:</strong> <%= @order.client.user.phone %></p>

    <p>If you have any further questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact the customer directly or reach out to our support team.</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for your continued partnership. We appreciate your efforts to provide the best service to our customers.</p>
      <p>Best regards, <br> The <%= @order.dish.restaurant.user.name %> Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
